description: This header file declares APIs related to Data Model Library support for objects in the MsgBusTestServer component, including functions to get and set parameter values.

methods.name: MsgBusTest_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets the string value of a specified parameter.

methods.name: MsgBusTest_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves the string value of a specified parameter.

methods.name: MsgBusTest_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets the integer value of a specified parameter.

methods.name: MsgBusTest_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Retrieves the integer value of a specified parameter.
